      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery through its six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS system. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring Bilstein dampers. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual and the factory M-variable differential lock. While showing minor patina consistent with its mileage, it is mechanically robust with the critical rod bearing service recently completed. A visceral, analog experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
