      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 luxury sedan that perfectly balances performance and sophistication. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in impressive overall shape. The exterior finished in Metallic Charcoal still holds a deep mirror-like shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood consistent with highway commuting, the body is straight and free of any major dings or scratches. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort. The premium black leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned and shows only light bolster wear on the driver\u2019s seat. It is a strictly non-smoker vehicle with no lingering odors. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium surround-sound system and navigation, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is top-tier. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule, with a comprehensive folder of service records included. The turbocharged engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes were serviced just 3,000 miles ago. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need a replacement any time soon. This is a turnkey vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy the luxury experience without the new-car price tag.",
